OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA fairly bright day with some
OL,6,Fsunny intervals. A few showers,
OL,7,Fespecially near the east coast at
OL,8,Ffirst this morning. Winds will be
OL,9,Fmostly light.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FStill the odd shower this
OL,12,Fevening then becoming dry with some
OL,13,Fgood clear spells developing tonight.
OL,14,FQuite cold with perhaps a touch of
OL,15,Ffrost in sheltered spots.
OL,16,
OL,17,CSaturday:FA mainly dry day with some
OL,18,Fbright or sunny intervals the best of
OL,19,Fthese around the coasts. One or two
OL,20,Fscattered showers are possible. A
OL,21,Fcolder day.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
